POST /plan

Request: { destination, start_date, end_date, budget, interests[], party, pace }

Response: { itinerary: Day[], hotels: Hotel[], rationale, sources[] }

GET /trips/****:id → returns saved itinerary + messages.

POST /feedback → { trip_id, dimension: 'usefulness'|'hotel_fit'|'pace', score, comment }

Tool Functions (LLM)

search_hotels(city, budget, amenities)

search_pois(city, interests, time_window)

route_time(origin, destination, mode)
